# RaithaBharosa – Smart Sowing Assistant

## Overview

RaithaBharosa is an Android application developed using Kotlin and Jetpack Compose to help farmers make better sowing decisions using moisture analysis and AI-based suggestions.

The app provides bilingual support (English & Kannada), farming recommendations, action plans, and Firebase backend integration.

---

## Features

* Login Screen
* Language Selection (English / Kannada)
* Sowing Index Calculation
* AI-based Farming Suggestions
* 7-Day Action Plan
* Farming History
* Firebase Realtime Database Integration
* MVVM Architecture
* Jetpack Compose UI

---

## Technologies Used

* Kotlin
* Jetpack Compose
* Firebase Realtime Database
* MVVM Architecture
* Android Studio

---

## Architecture

UI Layer → ViewModel → Firebase/Data Layer

---

## Firebase Integration

The app uses Firebase Realtime Database to store user moisture and crop input data.

---

## Future Scope

* Weather API Integration
* Room Database Integration
* Real AI Integration using Google AI Studio
* Advanced Crop Recommendation System

